ontend依赖CheckoutService\n   - 符合系统调用拓扑结构\n\n**次要异常的解释**：\n- adservice-1的错误率激增和aiops-k8s-04内存使用率上升可能是系统整体压力导致的次生效应\n- TiDB的io_util异常变化幅度较小，且在trace中未体现为主要瓶颈，与Redis延迟激增相比影响较小\n\n**结论**：trace数据明确支持\"redis-cart是根因\"的假设，Redis数据库操作延迟异常是导致整个系统级联延迟的根本原因。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "1d868f8e-347", "component": "redis-cart", "reason": "HMSET and HGET operations rrt_max spike (1.6s→29s) causing cascading delays", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "TraceAnalysis(redis-cart)", "observation": "HMSET rrt_max increased from 1.6s to 29s (17.8x), HGET from 1.7s to 28.9s"}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceDependencyCheck()", "observation": "CartService exclusively depends on redis-cart, forming propagation chain"}, {"step": 3, "action": "LoadMetrics(cartservice)", "observation": "AddItem rrt_max increased 15.2x (3.5s→54.1s), EmptyCart 8.2x"}, {"step": 4, "action": "LogSearch(redis-cart)", "observation": "No error logs found, supporting performance bottleneck"}, {"step": 5, "action": "NodePodMappingCheck()", "observation": "redis-cart-0 located on aiops-k8s-08 with normal node metrics"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
